Practical 3(A)
: Map Cosmetics


Steps to perform the practical:


1. Create a map i.e. Practical 1(A) and 1(B).


2. Press Ctrl + P → A new tab will open.
Name the file and open it.


3. Click on "Add Items" → "Add Map".
Drag the rectangle & adjust the map accordingly on the screen.


4. Add Label
Give a name to the label and change its properties.


5. Add Picture
Add an image from the computer (Logo of map).


6. Add Legend


7. Add Scalebar


8. Go to Layout and export the image, then save it in the folder.


